
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

If Resource is in Public IP mode, easy for hackers!

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Types of Secure:

1. JIT Access
2. VPN
3. Jump Box
4. Bastion

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

JIT Access (Just In Time Access):

* Open Port for access on demand, close automatically
	
VPN (Virtual Private Network):

* Only authorized users in private network can access
* Need software...etc so complexity is more

Jump Box:

* Place another VM in VNET, allow access only to this
* If i need to access any resource, we should connect Jump Box, then it connects required one
* Only one port open, bit risky since one port is exposed

Bastion

* Web Based connection
* No open Port is required 
* Simple and Secure
* Not FREE
* Requires Portal Access

-------------------------------------------------------------------------